  "pages": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_spesa_sabato/page_0.webp",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "ss0_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Saturday morning. 9:47. Nova Tutinia's IperPassata never sleeps."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex is in the trolley seat. Looking at the shelves."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He looks at them with the same expression a general has studying a map before battle."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_3",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "lex_pov",
              "text": "Shelves. Products. Endless aisle. Unlimited potential."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Favilla has no idea what's going on in that little head. She thinks he's admiring the colourful packaging."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_5",
              "type": "thought",
              "text": "What a good boy. Looks at everything so calmly.",
              "speaker": "favilla"
            },
            {
              "id": "ss0_0_tb_6",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's not quiet. He's planning."
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_spesa_sabato/page_1.webp",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "ss1_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Pasta aisle. Third corridor."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Inside Lex's head, something clicks. A memory."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_2",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "lex_pov",
              "text": "Fire. Mummy had turned into fire."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_3",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "lex_pov",
              "text": "It was beautiful."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex's eyes slide across the shelf in front of him. Tins. Jars. Pasta in bags. Products aligned in perfect unstable balance."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_5",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "lex_pov",
              "text": "If everything falls… mummy gets scared… mummy becomes fire."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_6",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Slowly, with the concentration of a rocket engineer, Lex grabs the dummy. Then the cord. Then the fabric bear on his bib."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_7",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Tongue out. Eyes serious. He begins to assemble."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_8",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "Mmmh. Mmmh. Mmmh."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss1_0_tb_9",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Favilla scrolls through the shopping list on her phone. Milk. Yoghurt. Tinned tomatoes."
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_spesa_sabato/page_2.webp",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "ss2_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "ss2_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "The weapon is almost complete."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss2_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex examines it with satisfaction. Dummy plus cord plus bear: structurally impeccable."
            },
            {
              "id": "ss2_0_tb_2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Favilla is three shelves away. Ten seconds of attention is all it takes and the plan falls apart."
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ],
      "choice": {
        "id": "attenzione_lex",
        "prompt": "Favilla is in her own bubble. Lex is about to launch his first military operation.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "tardi",
            "label": "Checks her phone. The list is long. Lex is fine.",
            "hint": "Of course she's fine.",
            "goto_branch": "branch_tardi",
            "stat_effects": {
              "segreto": -5,
              "resistenza": -10
            },
            "minigame": {
              "type": "lex_strike",
              "products_total": 12,
              "tiers": [
                {
                  "min": 8,
                  "label": "STRIKE! 🎳",
                  "stat_effects": {
                    "segreto": -5,
                    "resistenza": -10,
                    "legame": 15
                  },
                  "goto_branch": "branch_tardi"
                },
                {
                  "min": 3,
